div.span:
Create python env:
python3 -m venv env

Install python modules:
pip install -r requirements.txt

Bundle JS files & Run flask server:
npx webpack --config webpack.config.js
flask run

Rebuild database & Run flask server:
flask db init
flask db migrate
flask db upgrade
flask run

Install deps, bundle JS & Run flask server:
npm install -g parcel-bundler
npm i
npx webpack --config webpack.config.js
flask run
